GlobalPhiRotation.desc: Global rotation in phi; valid only for sense wires now.

ClockFrequencyForTDC.desc: Frequency (GHz) of the clock used for TDC, where 1.017774 GHz is 2 x (accelerator's RF).

OffsetX.desc: Offset x of the whole CDC wrt B2 coord system. N.B. Not fully ready; cannot control wire positions now.

OffsetY.desc: Offset y of the whole CDC wrt B2 coord system. N.B. Not fully ready; cannot control wire positions now.

OffsetZ.desc: Offset z of the whole CDC wrt B2 coord system. N.B. Not fully ready; cannot control wire positions now.

OffsetA.desc: Offset angle a of the whole CDC wrt B2 coord system. N.B. Not yet ready.

OffsetB.desc: Offset angle b of the whole CDC wrt B2 coord system. N.B. Not yet ready.

OffsetC.desc: Offset angle c of the whole CDC wrt B2 coord system. N.B. Not yet ready.

SuperLayers.desc: Number of SuperLayers in the CDC

FirstLayerOffset.desc: Actual first layer of the CDC

SuperLayerOffset.desc: Actual first super layer of the CDC

MaxNCells.desc: Maximum number of cells within one layer

NShift.desc: the shifted hole number of each wire in this layer

Offset.desc: wire offset in phi direction at endplate
